          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What is the best AI website builder for SaaS and software startups?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Framer is best for most early-stage SaaS companies due to stunning design quality (9.5/10), modern tech aesthetic that appeals to software buyers, and code export option for later migration to custom development. Webflow is ideal for B2B software needing powerful CMS for documentation, case studies, and complex pages. Mixo ($9/mo) works excellently for MVP testing with quick landing pages and easy A/B testing of different concepts. Squarespace serves B2B marketplaces and app sellers needing professional appearance with e-commerce for app sales. Durable offers fastest setup (30 seconds) for time-sensitive launches. For most SaaS startups: Framer for design and speed, Webflow for complexity and documentation, Mixo for rapid MVP testing and iteration.</p>
